Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:55.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You held out a small hand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:21:01.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Smiling like to you it was so natural
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:06.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It may have no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:12.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it is something I cannot do
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:18.39,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You touched my hand without thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:22.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it was nice for me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:30.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}All the time we believed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:35.98,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}that the world was in our hands
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:38.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}We were wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:46.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}maybe it wasn't 'cause \Nyou're holding my hand now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:52.57,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}At every moment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:21:58.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:03.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}I can believe, I can believe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:08.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}When I'm holding your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:15.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:55.49,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你伸出的手稚气未脱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:21:01.38,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}宛若唇边浅浅的笑涡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:06.55,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}它于无意中动人心魄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:12.32,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}无缘的我却徒添寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:18.39,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你漫不经心地触碰我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:22.18,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}殊不知暖流浸满我的心头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:30.50,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}回首昔日  我们坚信不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:35.98,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}手中所握  便是一树菩提
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:38.88,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}阴差阳错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:46.95,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}这一刻  世界也融化于你双手的温热
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:52.57,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}无时无刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:21:58.11,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}不论何处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:03.44,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}我的信仰  坚守不渝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:08.62,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}请让我贪恋你手心的温度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:15.99,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}手心的温度
